entries.journal_entry_completion_summary: You know where the rumors are coming from, although you need more information.
entries.journal_entry_description: Lt. Joth needs you to track down the source of some rumors about "dangerous things coming".
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: CorSec has heard rumors on the down low about some kind of trouble brewing. Talk to Ja'inn about those rumors.
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: Ja'inn mentioned a guy named Moril that has been doing some interesting smuggling recently. Unfortunately, no one has been able to get in touch with him. The Rogue CorSec guys do business with him regularly and one of them should have his contact information. They have a camp nearby.
entries.task01_journal_entry_title: Get Moril's Location from the Rogue CorSec
entries.task02_journal_entry_description: It appears that Moril was indeed dealing with the Rogue CorSec.  One of them had a data crystal with Moril's current hiding spot. Go to him and find out what he's been smuggling.
entries.task03_journal_entry_description: Look carefully through all 4 items in the next shipment. This may give you an idea about the kind of dangers that are on the horizon and why Moril is so nervous.
entries.task04_comm_message_text: Good work. Go to the drop location for the shipment and find out what you can about it.
entries.task04_journal_entry_description: Lt. Joth sent you a message: Good work. Go to the drop location for the shipment and find out what you can about it.
